        Creates a rotated shape from a Direction. Everything is based on the negative axes facing positive (Ex. minX to maxX, minY to maxY, and minZ to maxZ).
        Parameters:
        x1 - The min x for the shape
        y1 - The min y for the shape
        z1 - The min z for the shape
        x2 - The max x for the shape
        y2 - The max y for the shape
        z2 - The max z for the shape
        direction - The direction to rotate towards
        Returns:
        The rotated box shape
